name: 5v5

name: 6v6

name: Squad FPP
description: SQUAD, a game mode where you can team up in groups of 2, 3 or 4 players, or if you prefer, you can still play solo and take on everyone alone in the match.Squad FPP is based around your normal Squad game mode but instead of being in 3rd person this is strictly in 1st person.

description: Two opponents try to destroy all the other's buildings or army.

name: 5v5
description: Two teams of 5 players try to defeat their enemy by killing them or winning multiple team mini-games happening on the map.

name: Site control
description: The terrorists side tries to gain control of a bomb plant site to plant said bomb while counter-terrorist try to guard the sites or defuse the bomb. Each side can kill all enemy's to win the round.
